Maggie Blye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maggie_Blye 0 Maggie Blye (October 24, 1942 – March 24, 2016) was an American actress, also sometimes billed as Margaret Blye. She was best known for playing Michael Caine's girlfriend in The Italian Job (1969).
